MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
1. OPERATION ACTIVE ENDEAVOUR 22 OCT THRU 01 NOV
   IN THE MEDITERRANEAN SEA. NATO UNITS ARE CONDUCTING
   OPERATION ACTIVE ENDEAVOUR IN THE MEDITERRANEAN SEA
   TO PROVIDE FOR THE SAFE AND SECURE MOVEMENT OF VESSELS
   AT SEA AND TO DETER TERRORISM. IF CONTACTED BY NATO
   UNITS YOUR COOPERATION AND ASSISTANCE IN ANSWERING
   QUESTIONS WOULD BE GREATLY APPRECIATED. PLEASE REPORT
   ANY SUSPICIOUS ACTIVITY OR INFORMATION TO NATO WARSHIPS,
   TO THE NATO MARITIME COMMANDER, PHONE: 39 081 1970 6533,
   E-MAIL: OAENOW@LIVE.COM.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 02 NOV.
